name: Meet Me at The End of the Summer
description:
first from three of:
Seing The World as Red and Blue Series Collection
 
"when you wear glasses with the red and blue lenses on it, the lenses will tricks the brain and each of our eyes to sees things as a slightly different image. It is both immersive and astounding. But the glasses are not entirely to credit, it's our own brain that's doing most of the work - yourself."
